  "body": "Main focus: lightclient\r\n\r\nLightclient:\r\n- [x] Browser based prover with quasi complete support for JSON RPC API https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/4706\r\n- [ ] Publicly available infrastructure for consensus layer arbitrary proofs of any state\r\n- [ ] Write spec for slashing options\r\n- [ ] Ligthclients in L2 research\r\n- [ ] Consensus browser based lightclient over p2p\r\n\r\nRetain adoption:\r\n- [x] Improve user logging UX\r\n- [ ] Good peering and stable mesh in almost all cases\r\n- [ ] Increase average rated.network effectiveness from 93% -> to node operator average (~95%)\r\n\r\nNetwork features\r\n- [ ] Develop deneb HF https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/5279\r\n- [ ] In-protocol deposits https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/5366\r\n\r\nMisc / optimizations / debt\r\n- [x] Move libp2p instance to a worker thread #5447\r\n- [ ] Working PoC BLST on v8 thread pool\r\n- [ ] Good altruistic network peer (fast forward times, back-fill)\r\n",
